{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_153_79','text':"Gross Annual Value (GAV) of a property which is let-out throughout the year is determined in the following manner;-,;-,;-… ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_153_80','text':"Step 1;-,;-,;-… Compute reasonable expected rent of the property1 Step 2;-,;-,;-… Compute actual rent of the property2 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_153_81','text':"Step 3;-,;-,;-… Compute gross annual value (Gross annual value will be higher of the amount computed at step 1or step 2). ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_153_94','text':"Actual rent means the rent for which the property is let out during the year. While computing actual rent pertaining to vacancy period is not to be deducted. However, unrealised rent (*) is to be deducted from actual rent if conditions specified in this regard are satisfied."}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_153_95','text':"(*) Unrealized rent is the rent of the property which the owner of the property could not recover from the tenant, that is, rent not paid by the tenant. If following conditions are satisfied, then unrealized rent is to be deducted from the actual rent of the year:"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_153_107','text':"No Housing Loan ;Housing Loan taken for Purchase/ Construction of Residential Unit on or after 1st April 1999 for Self-occupation ;"}]},
