{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_130','text':"Question 3;-,;-,;-… ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_131','text':"Find out the encumbrance factor and value of the usable FSI from following particulars of the property;-,;-,;-… ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_133','text':"Land area – 533 m ;2 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_135','text':"Total built-up area – 205 m ;2 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_136','text':"Permissible FSI – 1 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_141','text':"Rate of construction cost – Rupees 5,000 per m ;2 ;Rate of land cost – Rupees 2,000 per m ;2 ;Desired rate of return – 9% ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_143','text':"Usable carpet area – 155 m ;2 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_145','text':"Monthly Rent on carpet area basis – Rupees 50 per m ;2 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_146','text':"Solution ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_147','text':"Cost of construction = 205 × 5000 = 10,25,000 Cost of FSI used = 205 × 2000 = 4,10,000 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_148','text':"Total cost = 14,35,000 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_149','text':"Desired Yield @ 9% = 1435000 × 0.09 = 1,29,150 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_150','text':"Estimated Yield = 50 × 155 × 12 = 93000 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_151','text':"Usual outgoings = 1/6 of yield = 93000/6 = 15500 Net annual yield = 77,500 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_153','text':"Hence, encumbrance factor = 77500/93000 = 0.833 Usable FSI = 533 – 205 = 328 m ;2 ;"}]},
{'title':'rb', 'content':[{'fname':'RB_h_166_154','text':"Value of usable FSI = 328 × 0.833 × 2000 = 546448 ;"}]},
